1 congratulate Senator Keturah Herron upon this historic occasion; and
2 WHEREAS, the success of this Commonwealth has always rested on its
3 acknowledgement and support of all its outstanding citizens; and
4 WHEREAS, the historic importance of the second African American woman
5 serving in this body is celebrated by all Kentuckians as a symbol of the shining
6 possibility that was spoken of during Reverend Martin Luther King, Jr.'s famous rally
7 outside the walls of this institution more than a half century ago;
8 NOW, THEREFORE,
9 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
10 Kentucky:
11 Section 1. This honorable body does hereby express its profound admiration for
12 Senator Keturah Herron for being the second African American woman to serve in the
13 Kentucky Senate and marks this day of the 2025 Regular Session as a landmark in this
14 Commonwealth's glorious history.
15 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in rightful honor and
16 commemoration of Senator Keturah Herron.
17 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
18 Resolution to Senator Keturah Herron.
